// CONTROL STATEMENTS

LOOP CONTROL:
	BREAK: BREAK THE LOOP

To Save a file in Mac while using nano editors:
ctrl+x -> Shift+Y

>>> string='India'
>>> for i in string:
...     if i=='d':
...             break
...     print('Current letter is: ',i)
... 
Current letter is:  I
Current letter is:  n
>>> 

OR

>>> while i>0:
...     print("Current letter is: ", i)
...     i=i-1
...     if i==5:
...             break
... 
Current letter is:  20
Current letter is:  19
Current letter is:  18
Current letter is:  17
Current letter is:  16
Current letter is:  15
Current letter is:  14
Current letter is:  13
Current letter is:  12
Current letter is:  11
Current letter is:  10
Current letter is:  9
Current letter is:  8
Current letter is:  7
Current letter is:  6
>>> 
